Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:45.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Numb your senses
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:48.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}No fairness is needed for pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Laughters above
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Playful smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Die get rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Bathe in sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My tomorrow is built upon your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Slay the last of your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:12.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}To reclaim what's rightfully mine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Each time we'll enter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}First time to make this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Final dungeon 無念な未来の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:14.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I have a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't part the rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Surround them, off with their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Christen my motive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}First time to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Final dungeon 群れて迷おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:24.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I hide among you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:25.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Facing my fire
